plot: After watching the appearance of Hyper Kabuto, Arata Kagami wants to get a hyper zecter too. He then approaches Tendou to learn the secret and tries hard to be like Tendou. However, he soon realizes that imitating somebody else is not the right way.
title: Kamen Rider Kabuto: Birth! Gatack Hyper Form!!
